title: Root and Shaw POI Amy Acker and Sarah Shahi
author: SHOOT POI
comment: Simply beautiful. I love the pictures and the song. The combination is really great. Amy and Sarah have great chemistry together. I find the chemistry of the actresses who play Elsa and Anna in Once Upon A Time to be just as wonderful and beautiful but it is more a sisters/close friends vibe. It is beautiful to watch actors who have great chemistry work/play together.
i want them to be together in real life also
